## Architecture Diagram

::code[lang=mermaid]
graph TB
    subgraph Input
        A[".surf file"] --> B["parse()"]
    end

    subgraph "Pass 1a: Front Matter"
        B --> C["extract_front_matter()"]
        C --> D["FrontMatter (15 typed fields)"]
    end

    subgraph "Pass 1b: Block Scanning"
        B --> E["scan_blocks()"]
        E --> F["Nesting Stack"]
        F --> G["Vec of Block::Unknown"]
    end

    subgraph "Pass 2: Resolution"
        G --> H["resolve_block()"]
        H --> I["32 typed Block variants"]
    end

    subgraph Output
        D --> J["SurfDoc"]
        I --> J
        J --> K["to_html()"]
        J --> L["to_markdown()"]
        J --> M["to_terminal()"]
        J --> N["to_pdf()"]
        J --> O["to_surf_source()"]
        J --> P["validate()"]
    end
::

