| `inline.rs` | 170 | Inline extensions (`:evidence`, `:status`) |
| `icons.rs` | 117 | Built-in SVG icon set (20 icons) |
| `lib.rs` | 112 | Public API exports |
| `serve.rs` | 37 | Axum CSS route handler |
::

